ES sched1
E s0(sched1)
Restrict s0 init1
P{s0}[F "d0"] <= P{s0}[F "d1"]
P{s0}[F "d1"] <= P{s0}[F "d0"]
P{s0}[F "d1"] <= P{s0}[F "d2"]
P{s0}[F "d2"] <= P{s0}[F "d1"]
P{s0}[F "d2"] <= P{s0}[F "d3"]
P{s0}[F "d3"] <= P{s0}[F "d2"]
P{s0}[F "d3"] <= P{s0}[F "d4"]
P{s0}[F "d4"] <= P{s0}[F "d3"]
P{s0}[F "d4"] <= P{s0}[F "d5"]
P{s0}[F "d5"] <= P{s0}[F "d4"]
P{s0}[F "d5"] <= P{s0}[F "d0"]
P{s0}[F "d0"] <= P{s0}[F "d5"]
